  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced", 
    "date": "2015-07-29", 
    "text": "Downwinders Compensation Act of 2015\n\nThis bill amends the Radiation Exposure Compensation Act to expand eligibility for restitution relating to atmospheric nuclear testing to individuals who were present, during the periods of testing, in any part of Clark County, Nevada, or any part of any county in Arizona that has a part north of the Grand Canyon.\n\nThis bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to eliminate the tax deduction for charitable contributions that are required to purchase a ticket to a college sporting event."
  }, 
